{
  "chapterId": "chapter-1",
  "title": "Chapter One",
  "items": [
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "zhLines": [
        "我的名字是以实玛利。"
      ],
      "enLines": [
        "MY NAME is ISHMAEL."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "zhLines": [
        "我可喜欢大海啦",
        "这是我超棒的冒险故事",
        "其中的一个哦！"
      ],
      "enLines": [
        "I love THE OCEAN",
        "and THIS is A STORY",
        "about one of MY greatest",
        "ADVENTURES."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "zhLines": [
        "在我决定踏上旅程的那一刻",
        "故事就开始了"
      ],
      "enLines": [
        "IT all started when I decided",
        "to go on A JOURNEY."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "zhLines": [
        "你知道吗？有时候",
        "我会感到有点烦躁不安",
        "我想去看看世界",
        "感受拂面而来、咸咸的海风"
      ],
      "enLines": [
        "YOU see, EVERY I get",
        "A FEELING — A BIT restless like",
        "I need to see THE WORLD",
        "and feel THE WIND on MY FACE."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "zhLines": [
        "于是，我把我的小行李箱装满",
        "前往海边的小镇"
      ],
      "enLines": [
        "So, I packed MY THINGS and ",
        "headed to A TOWN by THE SEA."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "zhLines": [
        "小镇的海边停满了",
        "大大小小的船只",
        "还有勇敢的水手们讲述",
        "他们在远方的历险故事"
      ],
     
      "enLines": [
        "THE TOWN was filled with",
        "SHIPS big and small",
        "and SAILORS with STORIES",
        "of brave ADVENTURES",
        "and faraway PLACES."
      ]
    }
  ],
